high_descs: Turn left then head to the trash bin
Pick up the apple in the trash bin
Turn right then head to the fridge
Open the fridge then put in and out the apple then close the fridge
Turn left then head to the counter with coffee maker
Put the apple on the counter in front of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled apple on the counter

high_descs: Walk to the bin to the left of the yellow chairs.
Pick up the apple from the black bin.
Walk over to the fridge on the other side of the room.
Put the apple in the fridge, close the door, take the apple out of the fridge, and close the door.
Walk to the counter to the left of the fridge with the coffee maker.
Put the apple down on the counter in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: To chill an apple and put it down on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go across the room to face the black bin
Pick up an apple from the bin
Open the fridge, put the apple on a tray, close the fridge, wait a few seconds, and take out the apple from the fridge
Turn left, move forward, and turn right to face the coffee maker
Put the apple on the counter in front of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple on the counter in front of the coffee maker
